{
  "stem": "23730.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was beginning of March, the night was, yeah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beginning of March-- if you sit up, it's enough.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You will be shot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because there are not enough guards to control these people, right?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that was the only way out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you sit up, you are shot at.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You are dead.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You have to lie in that cold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Imagine.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Two or three days-- four days, yes, and then we arrived at the gates of Belsen, a completely different side of Belsen.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the were the prisoners start-- I remember holding on to the, to the, to the, to the fence there, an elderly man, like a ghost, a skeleton.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we could hear him saying, don't come in here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Don't.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's typhoid everywhere.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we marched [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We marched in at the last few weeks in Belsen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The whole know-- the whole world knows the pictures and the movies, right?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to pull the dead bodies to the pit day after day after day.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There are young girls, hundreds of young girls, right, from all over the world, pulling them to the pit.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's very possible that I buried Anne Frank.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's very possible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She died in March, right?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She died in March and just two or three few blocks away from me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's very possible that I pulled her to the, to the pit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because all day we had to do that until we were so weak, you sat down.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And you said, enough, right?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was sent down by a German officer, Wermacht officer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the, the, the center of the pit was fairly empty.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because he hadn't got the [NON-ENGLISH] to, to-- so [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He send me down to pull the dead bodies towards the center.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He had a gun hanging in his hand.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
